Formerly know as gtest,

Change-Id: If95d302cbfd47ba3d63c6acbd008d6b01d0a3ec3
Bug-IoTivity: https://jira.iotivity.org/browse/IOT-2241
Bug-Tizen: https://bugs.tizen.org/browse/SO-1063
